Feature Pack 1 for Duet Enterprise 1.0, SharePoint components (x64) - DVD (Multiple Languages)
Files.Notes:
Release Notes:
  1. This download package does not include SAP Gateway 2.0, which is a pre-requisite for Feature Pack 1 for Duet Enterprise 1.0. You can download it by following the steps outlined in this SAP Note: 1626173.
    • Note: You will require an SAP account to download this pre-requisite software.
  2. Known issues
    • If you have installed SharePoint 2010 Service Pack 1, the Aggregated Business Calendar Web Part will not work. However, a fix for this is being made available in the December 2010 Cumulative Update. Once you apply this cumulative update, the Aggregated Business Calendar Web Part will start working.
  3. The following languages are included in this product: Arabic, Chinese-Simplified, Chinese-Traditional, English, French, German, Hebrew, Italian, Japanese, Portuguese-Brazil, Russian, Spanish, and Turkish.
